<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ṭūbay̱ liman̊ qad̊ ậmanūạ
 biạs̊mika yā ạb̊na ạllh̊
 fāi̹nãhum nālūạ bika
 ạl̊kẖalạṣa wāl̊ḥayāh̊

[V2]
 2- ạủs̊lim̊ta min̊ ạảj̊li ạl̊kẖaṭā
 ạủqim̊ta liltãb̊rīr̊
 fagẖufirat̊ lanā ạldẖũnūb̊
 biạldãmi yā qadīr̊

[V3]
 3- wāi̹dẖ̊ wuhib̊nā niʿ̊maẗa
 ạlại̹ymāni biman̊ qām̊
 faqad̊ tabarãr̊nā waqad̊
 nil̊nā ạlsãlạma ạltãạm̃̊

[V4]
 4- bika duʿīnā minãẗaⁿ
 lil̊mul̊ki wāl̊maj̊di
 fāl̊mul̊ku wāl̊maj̊du lanā
 biṣādiqi ạl̊waʿ̊di

[V5]
 5- bal̊ kulũ sẖaẙʾiⁿ bika qad̊
 ṣāra liqidĩysīk̊
 wakulũhu yaʿ̊malu
 lil̊kẖaẙri limad̊ʿūĩyk̊

[V6]
 6- fī ạlḍĩyqi fīka naf̊takẖir̊
 wāl̊maẘtu ṣāra rib̊ḥ̊
 fī ạlḍãʿ̊fi fīka nan̊taṣir̊
 lạis̊mika kulũ ạl̊mad̊ḥ̊</lyrics>
<title>ṭwby̱ lmn qd ậmnwạ</title>
</song>